In Blackridge there is some industry.These include the{quarry { Glossbrook}and the{sewage works.}
............
The quarry is between Harthill and Blackridge but it is mostly in Blackridge. The sewage works are just outside Blackridge on the road to Armadale. Glossbrook is just at the east end of Blackridge. Glossbrook mainly makes {various toys }as well as other components such as coffin handles. The factory{opened in 1977 }at Standhill, Bathgate. The quarry provides rocks for building roads. The sewage works are on the road between Armadale and Blackridge.
